Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview

        1.1. Limitations

   2. Dependencies

        2.1. Kamailio Modules
        2.2. External Libraries or Applications

   3. Parameters

        3.1. pretty_format (int)
        3.2. transport (int)
        3.3. fifo_name (str)
        3.4. fifo_mode (int)
        3.5. fifo_group (int or str)
        3.6. fifo_user (int or str)
        3.7. fifo_reply_dir (str)

